            "processed": "<p><strong>Big-FISH</strong> is a python package for the analysis of smFISH images (2D/3D). It includes various methods to <strong>analyze microscopy images</strong>, such <strong>spot detection</strong> and <strong>segmentation of cells and nuclei</strong>.</p>",
